%20measures%20the%20bank%20has%20taken%20over%20the%20past%20week%20to%20smooth%20out%20the%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20working%20hard%20to%20ensure%20our%20sites%20have%20the%20capacity%20and%20amenities%20employees%20need%20to%20return%20full-time%2C%26quot%3B%20Fusco%20said.%20%26quot%3BLast%20week%2C%20we%20had%20more%20than%202%2C000%20open%20seats%20available%20daily%20in%20Polaris%2C%20ensuring%20ample%20seating%20to%20accommodate%20all%20employees.%20We%20also%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20parking%20attendants%20and%20shuttles%20to%20improve%20the%20parking%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22503b6f44-a977-4895-9f30-52d2f2990d6a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELife%20at%20Polaris%20in%20a%20post-RTO%20world%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-return-to-office-memo-ending-remote-work-jamie-dimon-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJPMorgan%20CEO%20Jamie%20Dimon%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20his%20workers%20back%20to%20the%20office%20five%20days%20a%20week%20starting%20in%20March.%20The%20return%20was%20delayed%20for%20some%20office%20locations%20to%20give%20them%20time%20to%20get%20ready.%20The%20firm's%20Polaris%20campus%20only%20switched%20to%20the%20five-day-a-week%20RTO%20model%20last%20week%2C%20on%20April%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20isn't%20alone%20in%20demanding%20workers%20to%20return%20to%20pre-pandemic%20norms.%20Employees%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-demands-rto-five-day-week-no-remote-work-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-to-office-rto-banks-hedge-funds-private-equity-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECitadel%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20called%20back%20to%20the%20office%20five%20days%20a%20week%20in%202021.%20Tech%20giants%20like%20Amazon%20and%20TikTok%20have%20also%20ordered%20workers%20back%20to%20their%20desks%20Monday%20through%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-return-to-office-mandate-tech-talent-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolaris%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20pushed%20back%2C%20however%2C%20including%20by%20exploring%20unionizing%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-employees-return-to-office-enforcement-tracking-tools-guidance-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBI%20has%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamie-dimon-defends-leaked-town-hall-comments-rto-dei-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDimon%20defended%20his%20decision%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20internal%20town%20hall%20at%20the%20Columbus%20campus%20in%20February%2C%20saying%20the%20mandate%20was%20issued%20with%20the%20bank%20and%20its%20clients%20in%20mind%20%E2%80%94%20not%20individual%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20has%20addressed%20the%20insufficient%20parking%20at%20Polaris%20by%20reserving%20additional%20spaces%20at%20a%20local%20church%20about%20a%20mile%20away.%20Once%20parked%2C%20workers%20can%20wait%20for%20a%20shuttle%20that%20can%20take%20them%20to%20and%20from%20the%20campus%2C%20about%20a%2010-minute%20ride.%20Employees%2C%20however%2C%20described%2030-minute%20waits%20to%20board%20the%20buses%2C%20in%20some%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20one%20manager%20of%20a%20back-office%20group%2C%20on-campus%20parking%20has%20also%20become%20strained.%20The%20employee%20said%20the%20site's%20central%20buildings%20are%20encircled%20by%20a%20road%20dotted%20with%202-story%20parking%20garages%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20road%20has%20become%20logjammed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20moment%20you%20hit%20that%20ring%2C%20you're%20sitting%20in%20traffic%20to%20get%20around%20the%20campus%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20man