as%20widely%20spoken%2C%20and%20our%20kids%20felt%20welcome.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20our%20family%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20travel%20out%20of%20the%20US%20in%202023%2C%20we%20agonized%20over%20which%20European%20destination%20might%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-approved-tips-for-traveling-with-kids-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20place%20to%20take%20our%20young%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20were%20only%202%20and%205%20years%20old%20at%20the%20time.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20anticipation%20of%20what%20would%20be%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-countries-visit-with-kids-frequent-travelers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20international%20travel%20experience%20with%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20city%20where%20our%20energetic%20boys%20would%20feel%20welcomed%20and%20there'd%20be%20plenty%20of%20activities%20we%20could%20enjoy%20together%20as%20a%20family.%20We%20also%20wanted%20a%20destination%20we%20could%20feel%20safe%20navigating%20on%20our%20own%20without%20mastery%20of%20a%20foreign%20language.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20countless%20hours%20of%20research%20and%20deliberation%2C%20Athens%2C%20Greece%2C%20topped%20our%20list.%20So%2C%20we%20went.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20our%20trip%2C%20it%20definitely%20seems%20like%20the%20best%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-us-to-germany-now-vacations-are-all-local-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekid-friendly%20European%20travel%20destination%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20could've%20chosen%20to%20have%20a%20fun%2C%20welcoming%2C%20and%20educational%20adventure%20that%20our%20family%20will%20never%20forget.%20Here's%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227e0860f9-4c26-4506-ad25-a6f60766f1a5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20locals%20we%20encountered%20seemed%20to%20enjoy%20children%20and%20be%20patient%20with%20them%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20planning%20our%20trip%2C%20we%20had%20anecdotally%20heard%20horror%20stories%20of%20families%20getting%20excused%20from%20caf%C3%A9s%20and%20restaurants%20in%20other%20European%20cities%20where%20quiet%20adult%20spaces%20are%20protected%20and%20the%20presence%20of%20noisy%20children%20is%20frowned%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20our%20trip%2C%20we%20didn't%20want%20to%20feel%20stressed%20about%20our%20kids%20being%20loud%20or%20end%20up%20being%20excluded%20from%20enjoying%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20or%20nice%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20we%20found%20the%20stories%20we%20read%20online%20about%20Athens%20being%20kid-friendly%20proved%20to%20be%20true.%20Most%20people%20we%20encountered%20in%20the%20city%20seemed%20genuinely%20happy%20to%20see%20our%20children%2C%20and%20it%20made%20us%20feel%20welcome%20everywhere%20we%20went.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20locals%20treated%20our%20boys%20wonderfully%20%E2%80%94%20talking%20directly%20to%20them%2C%20fawning%20over%20them%2C%20bringing%20them%20booster%20chairs%20or%20special%20treats%2C%20and%20trying%20to%20make%20them%20laugh.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ebf5a8c-a61e-48c1-9e07-445449f8a45b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20found%20plenty%20of%20kid-friendly%20food%20options%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20hard%20to%20find%20food%20for%20our%20kids%20(and%20us%20adults)%20to%20enjoy%20in%20the%20city.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWarm%20pita%20bread%2C%20hearty%20souvlaki%2C%20and%20sticky-sweet%20loukoumades%20(fried%20dough%20with%20honey)%20made%20up%20our%20picky%20eaters'%20diets%20in%20Athens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20little%20one%20also%20enjoyed%20eating%20fresh%20chunks%20of%20tomato%20and%20cucumber%20from%20the%20(many)%20delicious%20Greek%20salads%20I%20enjoyed%20on%20our%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20even%20spotted%20a%20McDonald's%20in%20Syntagma%20Square%20that%20we%20planned%20to%20stop%20at%20if%20we'd%20gotten%20desperate%20for%20familiar%20food%20from%20home