%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20things%20haven%E2%80%99t%20changed.%20Growing%20up%2C%20Pushpa%20loved%20a%20good%20%3Cem%3Ejawari%20bhakri%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20flatbread%20made%20out%20of%20sorghum)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ethecha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F323084%2Fmumbai-mother-son-duo-start-aazol-maharastrian-traditional-snacks-help-rural-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20condiment%20prepared%20by%20pounding%20chillies%2C%20garlic%20and%20salt%3C%2Fa%3E).%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ethecha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20what%20she%20treated%20chef%20Amninder%20to%20on%20their%20first%20meeting.%20The%20dish%20instantly%20found%20favour%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fpalaash-farm-to-table-dining-1-1745847860.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20meats%20and%20vegetables%20prepared%20using%20the%20smoked%20bamboo%20technique%20are%20hailed%20for%20their%20flavour%20and%20are%20favourites%20on%20the%20Palaash%20menu%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fpalaash-farm-to-table-dining-1-1745847860.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fpalaash-farm-to-table-dining-1-1745847860-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fpalaash-farm-to-table-dining-1-1745847860-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fpalaash-farm-to-table-dining-1-1745847860-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fpalaash-farm-to-table-dining-1-1745847860-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C