%2C%20who%20noted%20it%20began%20managing%20money%20when%20George%20W.%20Bush%20was%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20declined%20to%20specify%20a%20specific%20figure%20it%20hopes%20to%20raise%2C%20but%20the%20manager%20believes%20it%20has%20a%20strong%20pipeline%20of%20potential%20backers%20even%20as%20the%20industry%20has%20moved%20away%20from%20single-manager%20funds%20and%20toward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-millennium-point72-balyasny-dominance-changed-the-hedge-fund-industry-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultistrategy%20behemoths%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhou%2C%20speaking%20with%20Business%20Insider%20during%20a%20recent%20interview%20in%20New%20York%2C%20stressed%20that%20the%20firm's%20long-term%20focus%2C%20in%20particular%20on%20companies'%20rising%20energy%20demands%20and%20the%20need%20to%20provide%20this%20power%20cheaply%20and%20sustainably%2C%20is%20still%20viable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20infrastructure%20for%20artificial%20intelligence's%20power%20needs%20has%20become%20a%20hot%20topic%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackrock-wants-to-build-the-infrastructure-for-ai-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebig-name%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20talk%20about%2C%20but%20Electron%20has%20been%20thinking%20about%20the%20burgeoning%20field's%20energy%20needs%20for%20years.%20Regulatory%20filings%20show%20the%20manager%20first%20invested%20in%20Quanta%20Services%2C%20an%20electricity%20infrastructure%20company%2C%20in%202019%20when%20the%20stock%2C%20now%20trading%20at%20nearly%20%24300%20a%20share%2C%20could%20be%20bought%20for%20less%20than%20%2450.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20power%20thesis%20is%20not%20changing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zhou%2C%20who%20joined%20Electron%20in%202005%20from%20a%20Columbia%20grad%20program%20and%20never%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20clean%20energy%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bfacing%20a%20lot%20of%20headwinds%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhou%20said%2C%20could%20be%20attractive%20soon%20as%20capital%20leaves%20the%20sector%20and%20valuations%20drop.%20The%20Trump%20adminstration%20has%20pledged%20to%20support%20the%20oil-and-gas%20industry%20and%20cut%20support%20to%20cleaner%20intiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20is%20%26quot%3Blike%20hunters%20waiting%20in%20the%20bush%2C%20waiting%20for%20the%20right%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhou%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20moments%20may%20be%20happening%20now%3A%20An%20investor%20document%20states%20that%20the%20firm%20is%20up%20more%20than%203%25%20in%20its%20long-short%20strategy%20in%20April%20through%20the%2025th%2C%20cutting%20losses%20this%20year%20to%201.8%25.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20down%20more%20than%206%25%20on%20the%20year%20as%20of%20press%20time.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20manager%20made%20more%20than%2021%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e2af6d1-ebe5-4196-b0ee-8554774f5c60%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShaver%20departs%2C%20but%20capital%20stays%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%242.8%20billion%20asset%20manager%20was%20started%20by%20Jos%20Shaver%2C%20who%20first%20ran%20the%20strategy%20as%20a%20standalone%20fund%20from%202005%20to%202008%20before%20joining%20Steve%20Cohen's%20now-shuttered%20hedge%20fund%2C%20SAC%20Advisors.%20Shaver%20then%20relaunched%20the%20manager%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20passed%20the%20reins%20to%20his%20longtime%20lieutenant%20Zhou%20in%20October%202023%2C%20although%20he%20remains%20a%20senior%20advisor%20to%20the%20firm%20and%20has%20a%20majority%20of%20his%20net%20worth%20still%20invested%20in%20the%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223643%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jos%20Shaver%20smiles%20at%20the%20camera%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680faa2aa466d2b74ab456c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225465%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJos%20Shaver%20founded%20Electron%20Capital%20in%202005.%3Cp%3EElectron%20Capita