0City%2C%20northeastern%20China%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20claiming%20the%20lives%20of%2022%20individuals%20and%20leaving%20three%20others%20injured.%20The%20blaze%20broke%20out%20around%20noon%20in%20Liaoning%20Province's%20Baita%20District%2C%20near%20the%20Sanlizhuang%20resettlement%20housing%20area.%20Emergency%20teams%20swiftly%20responded%20to%20the%20scene%2C%20confirming%20the%20tragic%20loss%20of%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2F22-killed-in-northeastern-china-restaurant-fire%2Farticleshow%2F120724888.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2F22-killed-in-northeastern-china-restaurant-fire%2Famp_articleshow%2F120724888.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2F22-killed-in-northeastern-china-restaurant-fire%2Famp_articleshow%2F120724888.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20federally%20employed%20military%20spouse%20and%20feel%20forced%20into%20retirement.%20It's%20making%20me%20sad%20that%20I%20voted%20for%20Trump.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hands%20holding%20an%20American%20flag%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6807fb38c6ad288d147ed652%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20federally%20employed%20military%20spouse%20feels%20she%20has%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20retire%20early%20before%20an%20upcoming%20move%20because%20of%20some%20DOGE%20actions.%20This%20picture%20does%20not%20depict%20them.%3Cp%3EDanielBendjy%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20military%20spouse%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20government%20for%2025%20years%20is%20retiring%20early%20ahead%20of%20another%20move.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERetiring%20gives%20financial%20safety%2C%20but%20she%20feels%20forced%20into%20the%20choice%20by%20the%20hiring%20freeze%20and%20DOGE.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20situation%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20it's%20impacting%20military%20families%E2%80%94%C2%A0makes%20her%20sad%20she%20voted%20for%20Trump%20at%20all.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20a%20federally%20employed%20military%20spouse%20who's%20taking%20up%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20on%20its%20Deferred%20Resignation%20Program%2FVoluntary%20Early%20Retirement%20Authority%20(DRP%20VERA)%20offer%20because%20she%20feels%20she's%20out%20of%20options.%20She%20has%20requested%20anonymity%20because%20her%20early%20retirement%20is%20not%20yet%20approved.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20her%20identity%20and%20employment.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWhite%20House%20Deputy%20Press%20Secretary%20Anna%20Kelly%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20has%20consistently%20stood%20up%20for%20our%20military%20families%20%E2%80%94%20delivering%20crucial%20reforms%20that%20improved%20VA%20healthcare%2C%20decreased%20veteran%20homelessness%2C%20and%20enhanced%20education%20benefits.%20His%20efforts%20to%20cut%20wasteful%20spending%20and%20make%20agencies%20more%20efficient%20will%20ensure%20our%20government%20can%20better%20serve%20all%20Americans%2C%20especially%20our%20veterans%20and%20their%20loved%20ones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%2025%20years%20of%20government%20service%20are%20about%20to%20come%20to%20an%20end%20%E2%80%94%20not%20because%20I%20want%20them%20to%2C%20but%20because%20I%20feel%20I%20don't%20have%20another%20choice.%20I'm%20opting%20into%20the%20DRP%20VERA%20before%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20move%20to%20Hawaii%20in%20June%20for%20his%20job%20in%20the%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20me%20is%20at%20peace%2C%20but%20another%20part%20is%20full%20of%20resentment.%20I%20feel%20pushed%20into%20this%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20pushed%20by%20DOGE.%20It's%20been%20such%20a%20stressful%2C%20emotional%20decision.%20I'm%20not%20ready%20to%20end%20the%20only%20career%20I've%20known%2C%20but%20I'm%20also%20not%20ready%20to%20stay%20behind%20as%20my%20husband%20moves%20thousands%20of%20miles%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20agree%20with%20DOGE%20that%20the%20government%20should%20get%20smaller.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-doge-cuts-federal-worker-firings-government-plan-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20things%20that%20can%20be%20cut%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20expected%20more%20organization%20and%20empathy%20when%20I%20cast%20my%20vote%20for%20Trump%20in%20November.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20I'm%20sad%20I%20voted%20for%20him%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2234294090-de83-4e67-99be-513ff5fc85e7%5C%22%3E'Doesn't%20feel%20like%20support%20to%20me'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20no%20stranger%20to%20military%20moves.%20My%20dad%20spent%2023%20years%20in%20the%20Navy%2C%20I've%20been%20married%20to%20two%20different%20Navy%20guys%2C%20and%20I've%20worked%20for%20the%20DoD%20since%20I%20was%20in%20my%20early%20twenties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20a%20new%20job%20during%20past%20moves%20with%20my%20ex%20and%20my%20current%20husband%20hasn't%20always%20been%20easy.%20The%20application%20process%20is%20long%2C%20and%20waiting%20for%20the%20right%20opening%20is%20frustrating%2C%20but%20it's%20always%20been%20possible.%20Federal%20employment%20was%20the%20safest%20option%20for%20me%2C%20a%20rare%20type%20of%20stability%20in%20a%20life%20of%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20feels%20totally%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmilitary-spouses-affected-doge-federal-job-cuts-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20says%20he%20supports%20military%20spouses%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20relocating%20during%20a%20hiring%20freeze%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20support%20to%20