22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Manohari%20Doss%20leading%20a%20session%20with%20the%20Federation%20for%20the%20Empowerment%20of%20Dalit%20Women.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXdDxxqZwIi8ld48izPW_IGdEPoaSch0uu9N0YpAZi7SuvTzbOnKecHOKa7f4LVVYacI8Ig8NtYSwfAajRviUv0u92R4a4tgkvoAu8byTUIoCSF20DOx1qUnUQDR2kRraISBmF2e4_nvfBSaGLdvZQ%3Fkey%3DBCUJIrS8KcwMTxxw9hAnrKID%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EManohari%20Doss%20leading%20a%20session%20with%20the%20Federation%20for%20the%20Empowerment%20of%20Dalit%20Women.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20objectives%20include%20ensuring%20access%20to%20quality%20higher%20education%20for%20young%20girls%2C%20creating%20dignified%20livelihood%20opportunities%2C%20and%20enabling%20women%20leaders%20to%20occupy%20positions%20of%20authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20federation%2C%20established%20in%20the%20year%202000%20and%20formally%20registered%20in%202024%2C%20also%20facilitates%20collaboration%20among%20multiple%20grassroots%20NGOs%2C%20conducts%20training%2C%20and%20builds%20alliances%20with%20broader%20progressive%20movements.%20It%20serves%20as%20a%20state-level%20platform%20to%20amplify%20the%20voices%20and%20agency%20of%20Dalit%20women%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManohari%20Doss%20has%20also%20contributed%20to%20advocacy%20at%20the%20international%20level%2C%20including%20bringing%20Dalit%20issues%20into%20the%20UN%20Charter.%20Her%20contributions%20have%20been%20recognised%20with%20a%20Laureate%20Prize%20from%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20World%20Summit%20Foundation%20in%20Geneva%20and%20featured%20in%20a%202004%20documentary%20on%20the%20Women%20Development%20Resource%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20her%20continued%20efforts%20and%20leadership%2C%20Manohari%E2%80%99s%20work%20illustrates%20the%20power%20of%20agency%2C%20investment%2C%20and%20training%20to%20create%20an%20upward%20spiral%2C%20where%20one%20empowered%20woman%20goes%20on%20to%20support%2C%20lead%2C%20and%20nurture%20others.%20We%20need%20to%20come%20together%20to%20recognise%20such%20efforts%20and%20support%20leaders%20like%20Manohari%20who%20are%20leading%20change%20from%20the%20ground%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fasvss.org%2F%5C%22%3EPrabha%20Yadav%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fngo.adaptnext.com%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNAVAJEEVAN%2520is%2520a%2520mass%2520initiative%2Cof%2520Bengal%2520sea%2520dwelling%2520people%5C%22%3E%7C%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fasvss.org%2F%5C%22%3E%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20Agriculture%20Development%20%26amp%3B%20Research%20Institute%20(ASVSS)%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fngo.adaptnext.com%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNAVAJEEVAN%2520is%2520a%2520mass%2520initiative%2Cof%2520Bengal%2520sea%2520dwelling%2520people%5C%22%3E%7C%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fasvss.org%2F%5C%22%3E%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20sugarcane%20belt%20of%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Solapur%20district%2C%20many%20girls%20grow%20up%20without%20completing%20their%20education%2C%20often%20dropping%20out%20of%20school%20early.%20The%20region%2C%20frequently%20affected%20by%20drought%2C%20presents%20significant%20challenges%20for%20Dalit%20communities%20who%20rely%20on%20small%2C%20government-allocated%20plots%20of%20land.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20limited%20livelihood%20options%2C%20many%20families%20are%20forced%20to%20migrate%20seasonally%20to%20sugarcane%20farms%20and%20brick%20kilns.%20This%20migration%20disrupts%20children%E2%80%99s%20education%2C%20particularly%20for%20girls%2C%20who%20are%20often%20pulled%20into%20cycles%20of%20exploitation%20that%20include%20unpaid%20labour%20and%20child%20marriage.%20Even%20when%20they%20remain%20in%20school%2C%20access%20to%20quality%20education%20is%20scarce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EASVSS%20was%20founded%20in%201987%20by%20a%20group%20of%20young%20people%20who%2C%20after%20spending%20time%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20returned%20to%20their%20drought-prone%20hometown%2C%20determined%20to%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20and%20work%20in%20their%20community%2C%20where%20migration%20and%20untouchability%20were%20widespread.%20Since%20then%2C%20ASVSS%20has%20worked%20to%20break%20the%20prevalence%20of%20school%20dropouts%20and%20child%20migration%20through%20community-rooted%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20established%20after-school%20education%20centres%2C%20provided%20tuition%20support%2C%20and%20created%20cr%C3%A8che%20facilities%20where%20children%20receive%20meals%20and%20care.%20Foster%20care%20and%20support%20for%20grandparents%20have%20helped%20create%20nurturing%20environments%20at%20home%2C%20while%20counselling%20ensures%20emotional%20support%20for%20both%20children%20and%20caregivers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20efforts%20allow%20children%20to%20stay%20back%2C%20remain%20in%20school%2C%20and%20reclaim%20their%20right%20to%20learn.%20To%20further%20curb%20seasonal%20migration%2C%20ASVSS%20has%20worked%20on%20improving%20agricultural%20practices%20through%20various%20organic%20farming%20experiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20sets%20ASVSS%20apart%20is%20its%20intentional%20commitment%20to%20inclusive%2C%20community-rooted%20leadership.%20Once%20led%20primarily%20by%20men%2C%20the%20organisation%20has%20consciously%20transitioned%20leadership%20to%20Prabha%20Yadav%2C%20a%20Dalit%20woman%20leader.%20In%20a%20region%20where%20girls%20were%20once%20unlikely%20to%20complete%20school%2C%20this%20shift%20reflects%20a%20broader%20transformation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20development%20has%20been%20made%20possible%20by%20a%20parallel%20shift%20in%20governance%2C%20with%20women%20from%20the%20community%20now%20serving%20on%20the%20board.%20When%20the%20ideas%20guiding%20an%20institution%20come%20from%20those%20who%20have%20been%20historically%20underserved%20or%20discriminated%20against%2C%20meaningful%20and%20lasting%20change%20becomes%20inevitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fngo.adaptnext.com%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNAVAJEEVAN%2520is%2520a%2520mass%2520initiative%2Cof%2520Bengal%2520sea%2520dwelling%2520people%5C%22%3EKalavapalli%20Lavannya%20%7C%20Navajeevan%20%7C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Telangana%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20generations%2C%20%3Cem%3Esafai%20karamcharis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sanitation%20workers)%2C%20many%20from%20Dalit%20communities%2C%20have%20been%20relegated%20to%20the%20degrading%20and%20hazardous%20practice%20of%20manual%20scavenging.%20Though%20officially%20outlawed%2C%20the%20practice%20continues%20in%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20sustained%20by%20caste-based%20discrimination%2C%20exploitative%20labour%20systems%2C%20and%20a%20systemic%20denial%20of%20dignity%20and%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%20injustice%2C%20the%20National%20Safai%20Karamcharis%20Finance%20and%20Development%20Corporation%20(NSKFDC)%2C%20a%20Government%20of%20India%20initiative%2C%20launched%20a%20programme%20promoting%20mechanised%20sanitation.%20In%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20this%20programme%20is%20implemented%20by%20%E2%80%98Navajeevan%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20grassroots%20organisation%20helping%20sanitation%20workers%20transition%20into%20safer%2C%20more%20dignified%20livelihoods%20with%20a%20guaranteed%20annual%20income%20of%20Rs%201%2C20%2C000%20per%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXff8ZP73dK_BbTvZAkIYqKKiQfh3L9zZO_NVduf2MvHz7ax5msMkC541oiKljzBacH6M2KNZRkb51MdPiEYLiF0kXZ36SUwrqM5kszLuD1-tTAUh4E3QOPNfJQkDM9OfENDx_AoRZ3MRfY1_DvBVuw%3Fkey%3DBCUJIrS8KcwMTxxw9hAnrKID%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESafai%20Karamcharis%20supported%20through%20NSKFDC%20scheme%2C%20implemented%20by%20Navajeevan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavajeevan%20is%20currently%20led%20by%20Lavannya%2C%20a%20second-generation%20leader%20and%20a%20Dalit%20woman%2C%20who%20walked%20away%20from%20a%20high-paying%20job%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%20to%20work%20with%20people%20who%20have%20long%20been%20ignored%2C%20stigmatised%2C%20and%20systematically%20excluded%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Esafai%20karamcharis%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20grew%20up%20participating%20in%20community%20visits%20alongside%20her%20father%2C%20K%20Sahadevaiah%2C%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20founder%2C%20and%20developed%20a%20deep%20empathy%20for%20the%20struggles%20of%20the%20community.%20Her%20leadership%20evolved%20naturally%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20she%20took%20on%20relief%20efforts%20and%20advocacy%20for%20sanitation%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20her%20leadership%2C%20Navajeevan%20has%20gained%20new%20energy%20and%20direction.%20One%20of%20her%20key%20initiatives%20has%20been%20focused%20on%20ensuring%20education%20for%20children%20of%20%3Cem%3Esafai%20karamcharis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20manual%20scavengers%20and%20waste%20pickers.%20She%20identified%20200%20children%2C%20provided%20them%20with%20foundational%20learning%2C%20and%20enrolled%20them%20in%20government%20schools%20for%20formal%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20model%20demonstrates%20the%20potential%20of%20what%20can%20happen%20when%20state%20resources%20are%20not%20merely%20directed%20%3Cem%3Eat%3C%2Fem%3E%20communities%20but%20are%20implemented%20%3Cem%3Eby%3C%2Fem%3E%20them.%20By%20placing%20agency%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20organisations%20like%20Navajeevan%2C%20the%20initiative%20lays%20the%20foundation%20for%20dignified%2C%20self-determined%20futures.%20In%20a%20country%20where%20caste%20continues%20to%20define%20the%20boundaries%20of%20opportunity%2C%20this%20collaboration%20proves%20that%20those%20closest%20to%20the%20problem%20are%20often%20best%20equipped%20to%20dismantle%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInvesting%20in%20Dalit%20women%E2%80%99s%20leadership%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalit%20women%20leaders%20carry%20a%20deep%2C%20lived%20understanding%20of%20the%20challenges%20their%20communities%20face.%20Their%20proximity%20to%20the%20issues%20enables%20them%20to%20design%20interventions%20rooted%20in%20dignity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20self-determination.%20They%20are%20not%20speaking%20for%20the%20community%3B%20they%20%3Cem%3Eare%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20despite%20their%20insight%20and%20leadership%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20grassroots%20voices%20in%20decision-making%20roles%20within%20institutions%20committed%20to%20social%20justice%20often%20reproduces%20the%20very%20inequalities%20we%20seek%20to%20dismantle.%20True%20inclusion%20is%20not%20just%20about%20visibility%20or%20representation.%20It%20is%20about%20power%2C%20who%20holds%20it%2C%20who%20is%20allowed%20to%20wield%20it%2C%20and%20whose%20wisdom%20is%20trusted%20to%20guide%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Dalit%20women%20are%20leading%20movements%20that%20turn%20caste-bound%20labour%20into%20dignified%20entrepreneurship.%20They%20are%20reimagining%20education%20for%20children%20of%20migrant%20workers%2C%20building%20statewide%20federations%20to%20demand%20systemic%20accountability%2C%20and%20shaping%20new%20models%20of%20governance%20rooted%20in%20collective%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20not%20isolated%20stories%2C%20they%20are%20blueprints%20for%20the%20kind%20of%20just%2C%20equitable%20society%20we%20must%20build.%20The%20question%20is%20no%20longer%20%3Cem%3Ewhether%3C%2Fem%3E%20Dalit%20women%20are%20leading.%20The%20question%20is%3A%20will%20we%20create%20an%20ecosystem%20where%20their%20leadership%20is%20acknowledged%20and%20supported%20with%20trust%2C%20resources%2C%20and%20sustained%20solidarity%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Dr%20B%20R%20Ambedkar%20reminded%20us%2C%20those%20who%20suffer%20the%20most%20must%20have%20the%20first%20claim%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stories%20of%20Manohari%2C%20Prabha%2C%20and%20Lavannya%20are%20just%20a%20glimpse%20of%20what%20is%20possible%20when%20we%20invest%20in%20the%20leadership%20of%20Dalit%20women.%20%3Cstrong%3ERebuild%20India%20Fund%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20committed%20to%20nurturing%20such%20leadership%2C%20supporting%20over%20500%20grassroots%20organisations%20across%20India%2C%20with%20a%20strong%20focus%20on%20those%20led%20by%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20growing%20movement%20that%20believes%20those%20closest%20to%20the%20problem%20are%20also%20closest%20to%20the%20solution.%20To%20discover%20more%20about%20the%20phenomenal%20women%20leading%20this%20change%20and%20how%20you%20can%20be%20part%20of%20building%20a%20more%20just%20and%20equitable%20future%2C%20visit%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frebuildindiafund.in%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frebuildindiafund.org%2Fen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Frebuildindiafund.org%2Fen%2F%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20article%20is%20written%20by%20Manohari%2C%20Prabha%2C%20and%20Lavannya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Dasra.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745581277000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXdDxxqZwIi8ld48izPW_IGdEPoaSch0uu9N0YpAZi7SuvTzbOnKecHOKa7f4LVVYacI8Ig8NtYSwfAajRviUv0u92R4a4tgkvoAu8byTUIoCSF20DOx1qUnUQDR2kRraISBmF2e4_nvfBSaGLdvZQ%3Fkey%3DBCUJIrS8KcwMTxxw9hAnrKID%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D423051%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manohari%20Doss%2C%20Prabha%20Yadav%2C%20and%20Kalavapalli%20Lavannya%20are%20leading%20powerful%20grassroots%20movements%20to%20advance%20Dalit%20women%E2%80%99s%20rig