out%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20course%2C%20trainees%20build%20decentralised%20home%20lighting%20systems%20about%2015%20to%2020%20times%2C%20gaining%20comprehensive%20knowledge%20and%20experience%20in%20running%20these%20systems.%C2%A0%20Once%20trained%2C%20these%20women%20hold%20a%20respected%20position%20as%20solar%20engineers%2C%20which%20empowers%20them%20and%20changes%20community%20perceptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost-training%2C%20women%20are%20set%20up%20to%20maintain%20and%20operate%20solar%20solutions%20in%20their%20villages.%20Small%20labs%20are%20established%20where%20they%20can%20conduct%20repairs%20and%20first-level%20check-ups.%20Upon%20completion%2C%20trainees%20earn%20a%20certificate%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Renewable%20Energy%2C%20recognising%20them%20as%20qualified%20to%20maintain%20and%20repair%20solar%20home%20lighting%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGo-to%20solar%20experts%20in%20every%20village%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20hands-on%20responsibility%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20with%20training.%20Women%20continue%20their%20work%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20ensuring%20the%20smooth%20functioning%20of%20decentralised%20renewable%20energy%20(DRE)%20systems%20within%20their%20communities.%20Harsh%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20systems%20form%20the%20backbone%20of%20energy%20access%20for%20rural%20households.%20Women%20in%20this%20role%20are%20usually%20less%20mobile%20and%20work%20locally%20to%20ensure%20the%20energy%20infrastructure%20runs%20smoothly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fempbindi-international-2-1745567785.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Post-training%2C%20women%20manage%20and%20maintain%20solar%20solutions%20indepen